Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到夏天了 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再去一次海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 夏天当然要去海边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要制造更多的夏天的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位 现在不是做这种事情的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天必须要做完暑假作业才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.78,0:02:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
